      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. what about hair? i've had some clients ask about how to handle different hair textures or more natural styles—like braids, locs, or just really curly hair—to make sure they don't look \"unprofessional\" or too casual in those settings. any specific advice for them?",
