      "content": "thanks. i guess i'm just curious why \"minimizing\" certain looks is the goal. like, wouldn't a natural texture or braids be just as \"neat\" as a straight style if they're well-maintained? do you think there's a reason why certain textures are often seen as less authoritative in the boardroom compared to, say, straight hair?",
